"{\"uid\": \"capitalfm.com-news-tom-daley-kids-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Capital  Will Manning4pm - 7pm  Nice To Meet YouMyles SmithDownload 'Nice To Meet You' on iTunes  News  29 July 2024, 19:50 | Updated: 29 July 2024, 19:54  Olympic Silver medalists, Tom Daley & Noah Williams!\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 208, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 90, \"end\": 96, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITunes\", \"score\": 0.9983734162253937, \"rank\": 0.0016292338562385834, \"text\": \"iTunes\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITunes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITunes\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"| AD  By Kathryn  Knight  Tom Daley's family were able to watch him compete in the Olympics in the best seats in the house.\", \"from\": 209, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6557595593128516e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom Daley joined the Capital Evening Show withJimmy Hillfrom the Team GB House in Paris to give us all the BTS action on the 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 334, \"end\": 343, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6557595593128516e-43, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999679712351, \"rank\": 3.2028827550172605e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 441, \"end\": 444, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"score\": 0.9999999868250599, \"rank\": 1.306548337349697e-08, \"text\": \"BTS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BTS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after Tom won his fifth Olympic medal alongside diving partner Noah Williams on Monday, winning silver in the men's synchronised 10m platform while his family watched from the stands.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 547, \"end\": 560, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"score\": 0.999998273608197, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noah Williams\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah_Williams_(diver)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom shares two sons, Robbie and Phoenix, with husband Dustin Lance Black.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 741, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 695, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"score\": 0.9987047735265933, \"rank\": 0.0012930976565693067, \"text\": \"Robbie\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Robbie_Jackson\"}, {\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9829816075963966, \"rank\": 0.016496901129522405, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}, {\"begin\": 722, \"end\": 740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dustin Lance Black\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dustin_Lance_Black\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking to our Team GB correspondent Sam Quek, Tom said: \\\"18 months ago I was sat on my sofa doing nothing and deciding to come back because my son wanted to see me at the Olympics\\u2026 now to be here with a silver medal, to be diving with Noah and to be diving in front of my family, it was really special.\\\"\", \"from\": 743, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 759, \"end\": 766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999759883437237, \"rank\": 2.3985307950870518e-05, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 781, \"end\": 789, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Quek\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Quek\"}, {\"begin\": 980, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"score\": 0.9780293241971193, \"rank\": 0.021320797451610918, \"text\": \"Noah\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noah\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sam asked if Tom's youngest child Phoenix might also ask to see their dad dive when he's old enough.\", \"from\": 1050, \"to\": 1150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1053, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Malone\", \"score\": 0.5202778404342011, \"rank\": 0.46193519091218466, \"text\": \"Sam\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Malone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Malone\"}, {\"begin\": 1084, \"end\": 1091, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9829816075963966, \"rank\": 0.016496901129522405, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom responded: \\\"I do not know if Phoenix will ever remember me being a diver, because he's only 16 months.\", \"from\": 1152, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1185, \"end\": 1192, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"score\": 0.9829816075963966, \"rank\": 0.016496901129522405, \"text\": \"Phoenix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phoenix_Raceway\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did throw his juice bottle from the balcony!\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really sweet to have them there.\\\"\", \"from\": 1307, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Tom effectively retired from diving after his success in the Tokyo Olympics, however, after a two year break he had a change of heart following a visit to the US Olympic and Paralympic Museum in Colorado Springs.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1508, \"end\": 1510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.901206488265317, \"rank\": 0.057374967092237814, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"score\": 0.7293047727182352, \"rank\": 0.3194628230961406, \"text\": \"Colorado\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colorado\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My son Robbie said to me, 'Papa, I want to see you dive at the Olympics', and that has kind of lit a new flame, and fire inside me, to want to see where this is going to go,\\\" he told theParis Olympicslast year.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1774, \"entities\": [{\"begin\